FBIS4-15030 "drsov066_b_94031" FBIS-SOV-94-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Issues Yeltsin Forms Western Group of Border Troops Yeltsin Forms Western Group of Border Troops LD0504192494 Moscow Radio Moscow in Russian to Tajikistan 1830 GMT 5 Apr 94 LD0504192494 Moscow Radio Moscow Russian BFN [Text] A decree of the Russian president on the formation of a western group of Russian border troops has been signed. The group will be subordinate to the center, with its directorate located in Voronezh. The objective of creating the western group of border troops is to perfect the leadership of border units protecting the state border with Ukraine.
